{
  "stem": "3952.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then abruptly, I stopped, saying to them, I could go on for four hours more, but I think I've made the impression on you, and I will leave it with that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that's how I got-- and they were standing up and giving-- giving me a standing ovation like five or six minutes, applauding in the-- in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This was something that-- that I'm very grateful for that I had this experience and reminded me of the kind of experience that-- that you can have, religious experiences here and now, even when you live well, in America.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We were-- we were on the way to Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were on the way from the [INAUDIBLE] factory to Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now, after the nine months in-- in Wolfsberg, which compared-- looking back, this was like Gan Eden and-- and Gihennum, like the hell and-- and heaven, heaven and hell, such a difference.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You come to Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Ebensee is a huge camp, meant for 20,000 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But there is a gathering of 40,000 people because from all the neighboring camp that were running away from the Russian-- from the Russian occupation, they came to Ebensee.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And Ebensee, they kept us in a quarantine block.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This was block number 26.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They kept us nude, nude, without clothes, without food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "One of the Greeks broke a window and stretched out his hand to get a little-- a little-- a little snow from the window sill, and they shot his arm.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "One of the Salonikans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We called them the Greeks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Salonikans.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They actually belonged to Greece.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It still belongs to Greece.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Salonika.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We were there for three days without food, without anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They would give us one-- one coffee, they would give us like lunchtime, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "For three days.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
